{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"iconStart","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/iconStart"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B32ThemeLinkComponentTokensProviderC9iconStartSbvp","roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"iconStart","extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"iconStart"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token false","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/iconstart"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"ic_theme_orange.png":{"type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}],"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","alt":null},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of links","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"link","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSLink"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllLinkComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LinkComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"links","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Link"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") and spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","abstract":[{"text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider/iconStart":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/iconStart","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/iconstart","title":"iconStart","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token false","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"iconStart","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"role":"symbol"}}}